                                                                                                                                Containers and layout

                                                                                                                                Modal sheet

                                                                                                                                Soon to be deprecated

                                                                                                                                Modal sheets are fixed, blocking sheets that can be used to deliver a message or help a user make quick decisions. There are 4 types of modal sheets, each with different content considerations.

                                                                                                                                Usage
                                                                                                                                Specs
                                                                                                                                Status & changelog

                                                                                                                                Metrics, type and color

                                                                                                                                Screen readers

                                                                                                                                VoiceOver

                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                1. Voiced preview:

                                                                                                                                "Dismiss, Button."

                                                                                                                                Label: Dismiss

                                                                                                                                Trait: Button


                                                                                                                                2. Voiced preview:

                                                                                                                                "Hey, I love you. Won’t you tell me your name? Heading”

                                                                                                                                Label: Hey, I love you. Won’t you tell me your name?

                                                                                                                                Trait: Header

                                                                                                                                Notes:

                                                                                                                                This should follow the spec for the Voice header component. For example, if there is a loading bar in it, it should read that too.


                                                                                                                                3. 🔈Voiced preview:

                                                                                                                                "The Doors band, Image, 4 faces, face 1, face 2, face 3, face 4, adult.”

                                                                                                                                Label: The Doors band.

                                                                                                                                Trait: Image

                                                                                                                                Notes:

                                                                                                                                “4 faces, face 1, face 2, face 3, face 4, adult” is reflecting Apple’s new image recognition feature in iOS 11. We won’t have control over how it describes the image.

                                                                                                                                The image needs to also support the ability to NOT be an accessibility element in cases where the photo is repeating content elsewhere on the modal.

                                                                                                                                Accessibility element? Yes | No


                                                                                                                                4. Voiced preview:

                                                                                                                                "Hello, I love you. Won’t you jump in my game?”

                                                                                                                                Label: Hello, I love you. Won’t you jump in my game?

                                                                                                                                Trait: Static text


                                                                                                                                5-8. Voiced preview:

                                                                                                                                "Tell me your name.,Button."

                                                                                                                                Label: Tell me your name.

                                                                                                                                Value: n/a

                                                                                                                                Trait: Button

                                                                                                                                Hint: n/a

                                                                                                                                Notes:

                                                                                                                                5-8 should follow button VO spec
